    @{
        ViewData["Title"] = "About Page";
    }

<main style=" display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            animation: slideIn 1.5s ease-in">
        @*Main Content of the Homepage*@
    <section style="background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            width: 300px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out">
        @*This is a depandable sub element that is reliant on the context of the website, it consists of the About Us Page, and the How it Works Page*@
        <h2 style="color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem">
            About Us
        </h2> @*Briefly describes what the bidding system is about*@
        <p style=" color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6">
            Welcome to Eduvos Online Bidding Experience!

            Are you looking for excellent tech deals? Look no further! Eduvos is excited to launch its Online Bidding System, a dynamic platform where you may bid, win, and save on high-quality used computer equipment.

            We believe in giving technology a second chance while making it available to those that require it the most. Our open and exciting auction system enables Eduvos to offer available equipment with a starting bid price, allowing clients like you to compete for the best prices in real time.
        </p>
    </section>

    <article style=" background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            width: 300px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out">@*Represents the dependent and independent content of the bidding system*@
        <h2 style="color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem">
            How it Works ?
        </h2> @*Detailed explaination on how the bidding system works*@
        <p style=" color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6">
                Browse and bid on available computer equipment.

                Watch as prices update in real-time—if multiple bids come in, you'll always see the most recent price.

                Get fantastic deals on trustworthy technology!

                Whether you're a student seeking affordable devices or a business seeking cost-effective tech solutions, Eduvos is here to help you find the gear you need at the best price.

                Join the auction, place a bid, and win big on high-end computer equipment!
            </p>
        </article>

    <aside style=" background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            width: 300px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out">@*Consists of the side content that is associated with the bidding system*@
        <h2 style="color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem ">
            Mission
        </h2> @*Brief description of the mission of the bidding system*@
        <p style="color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6"> The mission of the Eduvos Online Bidding System is to create an innovative, fair, and accessible platform for repurposing retired computer equipment.</p>
    </aside>

    </main>
